  "remarks": "MATSA (Mohandesi Toseh Sokht Atomi Company) is an Iranian company contracted to EU-designated Kalaye Electric Company (KEC) to provide design and engineering services across the nuclear fuel cycle. It has been procuring equipment for the Natanz uranium enrichment site.",
